title: High ping on OCE server
body:
I usually have around 22-26 ping normally but then the ping changed to around 80-95 starting early this month. 

I have already done multiple speed tests, spoken to my internet provider and they insist everything is perfectly good on their end. 
I have tried reinstalling League and still no success. 

Thank you in advance

replies.body: Same here, only mine goes up to a thousand + no idea why, ive had 2000 ping once aswell, but normmally reach 1300
